data.description: Welcome to this charming 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the desirable Bridlewood neighborhood. Once inside you will be greeted by an abundance of natural light. The main level features an open floor plan with an oversized sitting room that can be transformed into the ideal office space.  Across the foyer you will find the dining room that can seat 10+, which is fabulous for entertaining.  There is a well-appointed kitchen with a walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances, stained cabinets, ample storage space and center island along with a breakfast bar.  The kitchen has an adjoining breakfast area that is open to the family room.  The family room has a beautiful fireplace and large windows that overlook the spacious fenced back yard.  Additionally on the main level you will find an oversized guest room with full bathroom.  Upstairs is an expansive primary suite with updated touches in the ensuite bathroom.  There are 3 additional generously sized bedrooms with ample closet space shared by a large bathroom.  Another amazing feature is the upstairs media room with built-in storage. Upstairs also features a large laundry room with built in shelves.  This home includes two water heaters.    Located within a mile of shopping, parks, restaurants and schools.
